    <section id="buraidah-festival">
        <h2>Buraidah Date Festival</h2>
        
        <section class="event-details">
            <h3>About the Festival</h3>
            <p>The Buraidah Date Festival is an important cultural and commercial event in Saudi Arabia, held annually in Buraidah, attracting thousands of visitors to celebrate dates and their products.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="event-details">
            <h3>Types of Dates on Display</h3>
            <ul>
