    <section id="al-shanana">
        <h2>Al-Shanana Tower</h2>
        <p>Al-Shanana Tower is one of the most famous historical landmarks in Qassim. Located in the village of Al-Shanana in the Al-Badae'a governorate, it is a significant symbol of the region's heritage.</p>
        <button onclick="showMore('alshanana')">Read More</button>
        <div id="alshanana" class="more-info" style="display:none;">
